How to Reset PC1 IP Back to Empty

Click PC1 → Desktop → IP Configuration
Select DHCP → all fields clear automatically
Select Static again
Manually clear all fields to 0.0.0.0
Come back to Router and reconfigure


How to Verify Router Interfaces:

bashRouter# show ip interface brief
Expected output:
Interface            IP-Address    Status   Protocol
GigabitEthernet0/0   192.168.1.1   up       up
GigabitEthernet0/1   192.168.0.1   up       up


How to Reset Router Completely:
bashRouter# erase startup-config
Router# reload
Stuck in ROMMON Mode?
bashrommon 1 > confreg 0x2102
rommon 2 > reset
